snippet.title: Dig bombers! New Bombastic game
snippet.description:
Dig ahead, bomb away! 
Join real-time battles in this New game. 
Dig Bombers Features:

* Real-time PvP online multiplayer

* Arena. 4 Dig bombers in the same mine, this is bombastic battle.

* Dozens of bombs and weapons: 

Small and Large bombs, Cross Bomb, Filler Bomb, Vacuum Bomb, Jump bomb, Dynamite, Propane, Filler foam, Grenade, Rocket, Nuke 

* Customize your player with funny hats and boots. 
   Some of them will give you special abilities.

* Choose your character

* Variety of pickaxes

* Armor

* Portals

* Steel defensive walls

Get it!
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dig-bombers-pvp-digging-fight/id1383268892?mt=8
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spookyhousestudios.digbombers&hl=en
